<h2>Vol. 2: Most Wanted</h2>
<div class="side-by-side">
  <p class="big">
    Every good comic storyline needs a second chapter. After the resounding
    success of Tfue Tuesday, Tfue was eager for round two, and my team was ready
    to deliver.
  </p>
  <p>
    We adapted our original branding to align with Fortnite’s "Most Wanted"
    event, working closely with Epic Games on brand alignment and style. With
    just a week to develop this event, we prioritized utilizing existing assets
    and refining the branding to remain recognizably Tfue Tuesday, while
    creating a visual distinction that would excite fans for the next chapter in
    the saga.
  </p>
</div>

