<h2>Vol. 3: The Return</h2>

<div class="side-by-side">
  <p class="big">
    After taking an extended hiatus from the streaming world, Tfue returned to
    the spotlight with the third installation of Tfue Tuesday, just in time for
    Fortnite's OG event.
  </p>
  <p>
    I aimed to craft an announcement trailer that evoked a melodramatic comic
    book storyline - framing the story around his dramatic exit from the
    streaming world, and triumphant return. Working closely with Tfue, we pulled
    scenes from his viral break announcement, transforming them into a graphic
    novel-inspired journey that announced his comeback and the tournament all at
    once.
  </p>
</div>

